{"tid":1155844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊引述張曉明：修例合適合理合法　港人港審未必符合普通法","createTime":"2019-05-15T08:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T10:35:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e929df03125f07858fc74869c3d083ebbae1923e","tid":1155844,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190515/s00001/47caa345d77c1bf9daec09b6199255b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190515%2Fs00001%2F47caa345d77c1bf9daec09b6199255b0.jpg&h=ef43ee9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》引起爭議，正在訪京的民主思路召集人、行會成員湯家驊今早（15日）與港澳辦主任張曉明會晤，他在會面後見記者，引述稱張曉明表示，認為修例「合適、合理、合法」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊又引述張曉明稱，港府和中央政府都要做更多工作，以爭取港人信任，又認為坊間對於修例所關注的不少問題，其實都是不會出現的，因中央絕對尊重香港司法體制和司法管轄權。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊又稱，會面期間雙方亦提及有關「港人港審」的建議，張曉明認為建議不是完全符合法律原則和普通法制度。<br />\n<br />\n與張曉明會面之前，湯家驊曾表示不會主動提起修訂《逃犯條例》爭議。"},{"pid":"246418cc445870ab2e40304d56d3610ecdcae826","tid":1155844,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190515/s00001/1557905299369/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190515%2Fs00001%2F1557905299369%2F&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=5ddf1a64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190515%2Fs00001%2F1557905299369%2F&h=4a160dc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190515/s00001/1557905299369/</a>"},{"pid":"5e44abe1663b072e642c146e3cd417f618eb7a9c","tid":1155844,"uid":17765,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"首先衰十一嘅人要率先體驗陽光司法"},{"pid":"e3ddec1505086a08b4dac376bf2eea5e73683920","tid":1155844,"uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"